Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Loading Docks and Roller Shutter Doors

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer you 5,000-7,500sqm* of high clearance warehouse for sublease in the desirable location of Wetherill Park, minutes form the M7 & M4 motorways. 

Features include; 
 - 5,000-7,500sqm* of high clearance warehouse of 8-9.3m* 
 - 682sqm* of office and amenities
 - Access via three (3) loading docks and one (1) on grade roller door 
-  ESFR sprinkler system
 - Quick access to the M7 motorway 
 - Plenty of natural light into the warehouse
 - Available within 2 months notice. 

Please contact the exclusive agents from CBRE to organise an inspection. 

*approx

CBRE & JLL are pleased launch Wetherill Park Distribution Centre | 300 Victoria Street, Wetherill Park.

This is your opportunity to join Western Sydney's next premiere development located in the core industrial precinct of Wetherill Park.

 - Earthworks have now commenced
 - Project due for completion early 2021
 - 36m wide super awnings
 - 10.5m minimum to 13.7m internal clearances 
 - Multiple recessed docks and on grade doors
 - Space customisable to your business needs
 - Building 2 available: 12,279sqm*
 - Immediate access to key Northern and Southern logistics routes 
 - High quality constructed warehouse and office accommodation 
 - Prominent corner site linking Victoria Street to Greystanes
 - Minutes to the M4 and M7 Motorways

For further information please contact the exclusive agents.

*approx.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Drive through and drive around facility

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to offer a major freight and transport terminal to market in Western Sydney.

The building and site benefits from the below features:

+ Flexible lease terms will be considered
+ Competitive rental and incentive on offer
+ Building area: 13,700sqm 
+ Site area: 41,670sqm 
+ Internal clearances ranging from 7-20m 
+ Large awnings offering coverage for all weather loading/unloading
+ B Double drive through and drive around facility 
+ Surplus concrete for truck parking and storage 
+ Multiple on grade roller doors and dual access points for truck storage and linehaul operations. 
+ Detached corporate office and gate house 
+ Up to 180 car spaces on site

*approx

For further information please the exclusive agent Elijah from CBRE for a full information or site inspection.
